## 13. Data Quality Findings

| Finding | Severity | Detail |
|---|---|---|
| SMTP password in plaintext | High | `settings` key `emails` contains live SMTP credentials — must be moved to env vars |
| `patients.dob` as varchar | Medium | Stored as `'28-08-1995'` string, prevents SQL-based age or DOB range queries |
| Mixed FK types on `groups` | Medium | `patient_id` and `doctor_id` are untyped `int` vs `bigint UNSIGNED` elsewhere |
| No UNIQUE on `ai_interpretations(result_id)` | Medium | Multiple interpretations can exist per result — no deduplication guard |
| 2FA codes and TOTP secrets in plaintext | Medium | `two_factor_code` and `google2fa_secret` visible in dump — should be hashed/encrypted |
| Activity log `properties` always empty | Low | All 42 log entries have `'[]'` properties — audit detail hooks not wired |
| Duplicate German locale in languages | Low | IDs 3 and 11 both have `iso = 'de'` — data entry error |

